    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. RH index predictions agree with experimental measurements within acceptance criteria across validated operating points. High assurance level assigned reflecting comprehensive factor coverage, systematic grid convergence study exceeding MRL 2 requirements, and direct relevance of validation activities to the COU. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
